{"tid":803182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奧地利元首　率領60人　訪問香港　只有親子網站正常報導","createTime":"2018-09-02T05:19:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T02:49:20.000Z","uid":47714,"like":228,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"00416571fdedc3aa22798a2628df721a388af1d9","tid":803182,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:19:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ohpama.com/335297/overseas/monica-ng-%E5%A5%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%A9%E5%92%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E6%96%B0%E6%A9%9F%E9%81%87/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohpama.com%2F335297%2Foverseas%2Fmonica-ng-%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%2592%258C%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25A9%259F%25E9%2581%2587%2F&d=UwApLE9uCJ8z%2F58kAytvPU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=0ac90d8b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ohpama.com/335297/overseas/monica-ng-%E5%A5%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%88%A9%E5%92%8C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E6%96%B0%E6%A9%9F%E9%81%87/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ohpama.com/wp-content/uploads/master/2018/09/WhatsApp-Image-2018-09-01-at-15.32.04.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohpama.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fmaster%2F2018%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2018-09-01-at-15.32.04.jpeg&h=79ac7993&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n奧地利教育部長與楊局長會面<br />\n<br />\n對於港人而言，「奧地利」或許只是個旅遊勝地、音樂之都、莫札特等的代名詞，但對於當地政治則相對陌生。<br />\n<br />\n然而，港奧合作和交流或會成為未來新氣象。奧地利總理庫爾茨(Sebastian Kurz)剛於過去的週五(31日)，率領60人代表團正式訪港三日，隨行包括奧地利教育部部長、經濟部部長、創科部部長及其內閣、大學代表、企業代表和奧地利媒體，特首林鄭月娥當日與庫爾茨會面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ohpama.com/wp-content/uploads/master/2018/09/12346yuio.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohpama.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fmaster%2F2018%2F09%2F12346yuio.jpg&h=7f524ea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n庫爾茨又被稱為「神奇小子」，去年11月以反移民立場成功當選奧地利總理，現年僅32歲，是全歐洲最年輕的國家領袖。此行不但會見港府有關局長，還參觀了香港理工大學、香港培正中學、香港科技園、數碼港等，目的是促進奧港在創新科技、教育、發展、智慧城市等的機遇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ohpama.com/wp-content/uploads/master/2018/09/IMG_8620-686x515.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohpama.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fmaster%2F2018%2F09%2FIMG_8620-686x515.jpg&h=65e775f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鑒於培正中學校長早前曾到訪奧地利，了解當地校園生活，而且該校於STEM教育表現優秀，又有畢業生選擇到奧地利升學，更有畢業生成為諾貝爾獎得主，可見培正中學與奧地利關係密切，而且表現出色，故奧地利總理代表團選擇到該校訪問。<br />\n<br />\n盼望奧地利總理此行能創造更多奧港合作新機遇，促進兩地文化交流的同時，亦加強兩地的資訊科技和數碼化發展和合作。"},{"pid":"413abad5c8a4fc3ec7b176d50f931deb3f5a620d","tid":803182,"uid":64601,"like":150,"dislike":1,"score":149,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:26:14.000Z","msg":"係咁架啦，tbb淨係報中國新聞"},{"pid":"9e32ccf3df3e8363a48a64ca2ce03b1315e53c78","tid":803182,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:27:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> pish"},{"pid":"0e4087dbfa68109e7a3ead1f09046066f4fd48e9","tid":803182,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e97fcc80588b524c27084d4b09b437dbe1c1c20","tid":803182,"uid":89931,"like":190,"dislike":0,"score":190,"quote":{"pid":"413abad5c8a4fc3ec7b176d50f931deb3f5a620d","tid":803182,"uid":64601,"like":150,"dislike":1,"score":149,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:26:14.000Z","msg":"係咁架啦，tbb淨係報中國新聞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:28:21.000Z","msg":"no no no 仲有播美國水災美國槍擊案美國政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e254c521099ad8951f8ac9009f052ae2cc67a196","tid":803182,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":346,"score":-345,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:28:59.000Z","msg":"奧地利？ 唔知點解硬係比人一種係八婆個契仔既地名"},{"pid":"79ea09d54b3dbc38806e3bcf67fb366fac338c72","tid":803182,"uid":52817,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"e254c521099ad8951f8ac9009f052ae2cc