物到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:51:16.000Z","msg":"blocked呢啲暑假仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9467ace6ccd049b232a1637d96cbffed8d4fe7a","tid":803182,"uid":65429,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:56:45.000Z","msg":"個鬼佬有冇200CM?"},{"pid":"fd6613cf49edeb78e380c067311c5b9db2ac393c","tid":803182,"uid":61853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eafcd40e2aee8eacde7f489e5b812e70b3b61ea0","tid":803182,"uid":40216,"like":22,"dislike":63,"score":-41,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:44:38.000Z","msg":"九成港人澳洲同奧地利都未識分啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:56:58.000Z","msg":"歷史堂點都聽過呀"},{"pid":"60006586b055d0c90bb10cfaa544ef1f59159955","tid":803182,"uid":4574,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T06:03:22.000Z","msg":"呢啲先係優秀國家<br />\n<br />\n一帶一路班垃圾<br />\n加埋都無用"},{"pid":"f2e809ee6d9693fe3e2dfe9f0da22d0e06787a00","tid":803182,"uid":47714,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T06:05:09.000Z","msg":"但係相中學校係香港加拿大國際學校<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cdnis.edu.hk/news/federal-chancellor-austria-visits-cdnis\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdnis.edu.hk%2Fnews%2Ffederal-chancellor-austria-visits-cdnis&d=UwApLE9uCJ8z%2F58kAytvPU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=6ee69cd9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cdnis.edu.hk/news/federal-chancellor-austria-visits-cdnis</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AhZN9VY3-7I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAhZN9VY3-7I&d=UwApLE9uCJ8z%2F58kAytvPU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=36f8d7bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AhZN9VY3-7I</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢間先係培正中學<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DmAW-ZQXsAIVnGI.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDmAW-ZQXsAIVnGI.jpg%3Alarge&h=fa52db56&