插大灣區<br />\n似乎同違背中國當局規劃都有關係</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b708e4faa1c274fc7c374af637e266d7c1400b54","tid":803182,"uid":67043,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:01:35.000Z","msg":"佢交流嘅對象全部親中到仆街，分分鐘係統戰部靠香港拉攏奧地利"},{"pid":"211524395d34a7a8a1ca7eb1191c0fe51b08ce80","tid":803182,"uid":99962,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:05:43.000Z","msg":"香港人除左錢同利益之外會理其他野既咩？"},{"pid":"6b45408688e83a0bdc53d27b6f3ce54b7cc8f981","tid":803182,"uid":47714,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"b708e4faa1c274fc7c374af637e266d7c1400b54","tid":803182,"uid":67043,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:01:35.000Z","msg":"佢交流嘅對象全部親中到仆街，分分鐘係統戰部靠香港拉攏奧地利"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:17:54.000Z","msg":"係培正　唔係培僑o波"},{"pid":"32e83ef045bf63722c6ba2ae2610ec1cd434bba7","tid":803182,"uid":151496,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9e97fcc80588b524c27084d4b09b437dbe1c1c20","tid":803182,"uid":89931,"like":190,"dislike":0,"score":190,"quote":{"pid":"413abad5c8a4fc3ec7b176d50f931deb3f5a620d","tid":803182,"uid":64601,"like":150,"dislike":1,"score":149,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:26:14.000Z","msg":"係咁架啦，tbb淨係報中國新聞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T05:28:21.000Z","msg":"no no no 仲有播美國水災美國槍擊案美國政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:24:43.000Z","msg":"仲有臺灣，日本風災，水災"},{"pid":"7974bc6de72caa8450918126bd0857f3ecda48d9","tid":803182,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T07:28:21.000Z","msg":"以前曾蔭權時代點會唔報呢類新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0934e209c6f9e020ba499df7e0395052c8d636","tid":803182,"uid":389,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f2e809ee6d9693fe3e2dfe9f0da22d0e06787a00","tid":803182,"uid":47714,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T06:05:09.000Z","msg":"但係相中學校係香港加拿大國際學校<br />\n<a hr